Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.99,0:00:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原…原腸動物？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.99,0:00:32.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(436,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.58,0:00:49.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,駐紮地…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OP
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}東京區域第39區
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.44,0:02:48.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs21}第3臨時小學
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:52.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,400)\pos(646,388)\fsp3\bord0}#08 境界線的石碑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.61,0:02:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 我是從今天起給你們當老師的里見蓮太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.47,0:02:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愛好是觀察昆蟲 採集植物
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.53,0:02:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,另外也喜歡微生物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.18,0:03:02.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還會一些格鬥技
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.46,0:03:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們有什麼問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.80,0:03:07.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你加油 里見老師
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.75,0:03:12.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎麼害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.44,0:03:14.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接受委託來給這些孩子當老師的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.92,0:03:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不正是里見你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:18.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 那邊那位
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.10,0:03:19.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.93,0:03:24.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽說老師和延珠是以結婚為前提同居的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.13,0:03:25.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.20,0:03:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.63,0:03:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎麼可能呢 她只是個食客
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼換另一位老師吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:37.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我是天童木更
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.38,0:03:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.63,0:03:41.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 老師！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.50,0:03:42.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽延珠說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.54,0:03:46.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你因為胸部太大 連腳下都看不到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.97,0:03:48.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:48.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.97,0:03:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,木更老師和蓮太郎老師正在交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.47,0:03:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們會結婚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.15,0:03:58.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們沒有交往 更不會結婚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.80,0:04:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 那麼東京區域的統治者就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.52,0:04:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\pos(760,10)\fs25\bord0\1c&HFFFFFF&}原腸動物新法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是聖天子大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.07,0:04:12.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回答正確
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.25,0:04:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒見過聖天子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖天子大人就是那傢伙喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.70,0:04:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聖天子大人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.19,0:04:24.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,貴安 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.50,0:04:27.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上學開心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨石碑會倒塌？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天晚上 貼附在32號巨石碑上的是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.27,0:04:42.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,階段Ⅳ 通稱畢宿五
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為它注入的錵侵蝕液
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.02,0:04:45.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(467,437)\fs21}Varanium
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:49.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六天後 32號巨石碑就會失去磁場 進而倒塌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:55.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,製作替代巨石碑的工作已經開始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.97,0:04:58.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但直到完成 還要花費九天時間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.43,0:05:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,根據分析 在巨石碑倒塌後三天內
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湧入的原腸動物會導致
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.14,0:05:04.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(422,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.69,0:05:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,東京區域的全體市民死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或者原腸動物化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:08.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(438,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.37,0:05:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了防止造成恐慌 我們已經實施了信息管制
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.02,0:05:18.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是幾天後巨石碑便會開始白化
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.12,0:05:22.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這件事不可能一直隱瞞下去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨石碑之外已經逐漸聚集了將近2000隻原腸動物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.50,0:05:28.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(675,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.00,0:05:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說2000隻？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.60,0:05:33.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是畢宿五號令著它們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.91,0:05:38.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下 階段Ⅳ的畢宿五為什麼會貼附在巨石碑上？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了階段Ⅴ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:43.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他原腸動物不是都會受到巨石碑磁場的影響嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.71,0:05:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(230,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.10,0:05:45.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這點尚不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.15,0:05:51.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且蟻型似乎是為了給畢宿五爭取時間才闖進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.27,0:05:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主動選擇死亡的自我犧牲…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.96,0:05:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你想讓我做些什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.63,0:06:01.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我希望你組織「輔助部隊」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輔助…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.45,0:06:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,輔助部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.75,0:06:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,指的是把民警編入自衛隊的分隊系統
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:09.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是讓我組織隊伍進行戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:17.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里見先生 我希望你成為民警分隊的隊長 參加決戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.08,0:06:20.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,決戰…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:24.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從巨石碑倒塌後到替代巨石碑建成為止這三天之內
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對入侵的原腸動物一個不剩地進行迎擊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.38,0:06:28.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(350,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:32.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是關係到東京區域命運的決戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.78,0:06:43.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有六天
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.25,0:06:45.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這東京區域就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.80,0:06:48.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切就像假的一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對你的心 天誅天誅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.78,0:07:01.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let me go 無論何時
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.35,0:07:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來今天蒂娜會過來住呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:06.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.91,0:07:09.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,頭暈目眩了吧 怎麼樣 蓮太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.75,0:07:14.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 蓮太郎先生 請嚐嚐看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:19.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.77,0:07:21.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的 好好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:25.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎 那麼下次就做鳳尾魚披薩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.10,0:07:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的菜呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:28.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:32.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就做卡爾博納拉披薩 或者海鮮披薩…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:34.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全是披薩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.37,0:07:36.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只會做披薩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.17,0:07:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的假的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.14,0:07:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還醒著嗎 蓮太郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.49,0:07:53.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你睡不著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.43,0:08:00.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然知道「天誅少女」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.86,0:08:04.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,延珠讓我看了第一季全集
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.69,0:08:07.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我見識到了日本動畫的精髓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:08.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有那麼誇張嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.50,0:08:16.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感謝蓮太郎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.11,0:08:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果留在蘭德教授身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定無法體驗到這夢幻般的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.76,0:08:25.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒂娜…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.50,0:08:31.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直想要蓮太郎先生這樣的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.60,0:08:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能叫你哥哥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.64,0:08:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:43.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒂娜 不許搶先
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.34,0:08:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:55.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是有話要說嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.55,0:09:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.68,0:09:04.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巨石碑會倒塌…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.86,0:09:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不吃驚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.06,0:09:08.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很吃驚 但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.41,0:09:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們要做的事還是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.05,0:09:11.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.27,0:09:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會告訴延珠的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.36,0:09:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那傢伙一定會說「我也要戰鬥」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.06,0:09:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的甘願這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:23.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,排名98位的蒂娜·斯普朗特
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:26.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在和哥哥的戰鬥中曾經死過一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.12,0:09:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在我已重獲新生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請你隨意差遣我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:41.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我還以為終於能過上一段和平的日子了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.88,0:09:47.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一年前 我和木更小姐為了復仇
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.99,0:09:49.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成立了天童民間警備公司
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.35,0:09:53.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個時候 在我的心中
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有對原腸動物的憎惡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(421,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.80,0:09:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和延珠初次相遇的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:01.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那傢伙被人類背叛了許多次
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,眼神比我們更加冰冷乾枯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:08.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那之後僅僅一年就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先是我和延珠改變了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.08,0:10:16.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後影響了木更小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.39,0:10:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天童社長乍看之下似乎很溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:22.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.05,0:10:26.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 今天先睡覺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.09,0:10:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼請讓我用你的手臂當枕頭 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.07,0:10:30.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.88,0:10:46.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 里見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.76,0:10:49.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 木更
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.49,0:10:50.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.80,0:10:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說你還是在進門前先說「我要進來了」好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.40,0:10:55.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我是來讓你把蒂娜還給我的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.02,0:11:01.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 蒂娜在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.55,0:11:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:15.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早上好 昨晚真愉快呢 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.40,0:11:18.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然哥哥有時很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是教了我許多東西 我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.75,0:11:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒂娜？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.11,0:11:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來報警…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.27,0:11:29.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.36,0:11:31.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是和「夜間模式的蒂娜」一起聊了聊天而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼夜間模式啊 變態！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.65,0:11:36.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被蒂娜搶先了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.97,0:11:39.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.38,0:11:52.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「被詛咒的孩子」排斥運動的東京區域分部長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.36,0:11:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨晚遭不明人士襲擊身亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.43,0:12:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目擊者稱犯人是出身於外圍區的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.64,0:12:01.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,針對「被詛咒的孩子」的輿論將會日益嚴厲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:05.56,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,未來走向？原腸動物新法
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「原腸動物新法」在這件事影響下 幾乎不可能通過了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.07,0:12:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(169,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:15.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 你給松崎老師打電話了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自從上次那件事以來 社會騷動不安
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.92,0:12:21.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天不睏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.15,0:12:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最近我正在逐漸把生物鐘調整為日間模式
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.34,0:12:31.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來我們要去做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去招募同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.03,0:12:34.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這次不是以搭檔的形式作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是把分隊組織起來 和原腸動物軍團戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(515,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.48,0:12:41.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不募集同伴 就連戰鬥都無法參加了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.20,0:12:43.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…為什麼要帶上我？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.26,0:12:46.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是現在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:49.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕就沒機會帶你逛東京區域了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:52.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想去哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和哥哥…約會
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.11,0:12:58.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.10,0:12:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.46,0:13:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉 只能送你那種東西作為禮物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.33,0:13:47.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 我很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.69,0:13:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會一輩子好好珍惜它的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.45,0:13:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我聽到了歌聲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.83,0:14:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs25\1c&H000000&\bord0}我是外圍區的被詛咒的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:04.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.40,0:14:13.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的眼睛怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:17.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你是被詛咒的孩子 那應該不會生病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.40,0:14:26.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的眼睛灌了鉛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.07,0:14:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的媽媽拋棄了我 她討厭我的紅眼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.46,0:14:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是被詛咒的孩子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:42.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是怎麼知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.10,0:14:44.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.72,0:14:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我只有乞求別人才能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.90,0:14:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以除了像這樣微笑以外
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.23,0:14:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道露出什麼表情才好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.37,0:14:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.38,0:15:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還真是過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:04.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又不是我 是你幹的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:07.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我勸你最近還是不要來這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.10,0:15:10.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…我還有妹妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.20,0:15:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼多錢…為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要說了 跟我約好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.22,0:15:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要寬恕原腸動物！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:36.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(467,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要寬恕原腸動物！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.60,0:15:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(467,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.35,0:15:41.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把被詛咒的孩子趕出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:43.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把被詛咒的孩子趕出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要寬恕原腸動物！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.26,0:15:45.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(467,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要寬恕原腸動物！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:48.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(467,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.51,0:15:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25\1c&H000000&\bord0}不允許原腸動物因子存在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.24,0:15:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs25\1c&H317EDC&\bord0}「原腸動物新法」提案廢棄
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.47,0:15:50.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把被詛咒的孩子趕出去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.60,0:15:58.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 有人在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.42,0:16:06.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是變態里見蓮太郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.23,0:16:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是片桐妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.63,0:16:11.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫弓月 可惡的FUCKIN'變態
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:12.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.39,0:16:15.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自從影胤騷亂後我們就沒見過面了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有三個月了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.54,0:16:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你似乎出人頭地了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 難道是來挖苦我們的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.89,0:16:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來找你哥哥談工作的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.13,0:16:26.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不需要變態施捨的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.20,0:16:35.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來你們生意興隆 片桐兄
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.49,0:16:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別諷刺我了 BOY
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.39,0:16:40.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.13,0:16:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實際上是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.42,0:16:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來猜猜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.40,0:16:47.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為巨石碑倒塌這種超FUCKIN'的劇本逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:51.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你只好無奈地到處找人組成輔助部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.60,0:16:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果全都吃了閉門羹
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.09,0:16:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最後無計可施只好到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:16:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:16:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說對了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:04.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像你這種一夜暴富的小鬼 只會惹整個區域的民警討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.60,0:17:05.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:09.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說吧 什麼時候倒塌 獵物有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,新聞雖然還沒播出
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.72,0:17:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過巨石碑倒塌是在四天之後
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.23,0:17:14.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敵人有兩千
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.52,0:17:15.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四天後？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:18.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩千？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.72,0:17:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出口就在後面
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.28,0:17:24.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弓月 客人要回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.05,0:17:27.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果什麼都不做 東京區域就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.53,0:17:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你們也會死
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.70,0:17:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,畢宿五那傢伙是恐怖的怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:41.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它從前把三座城市變成廢墟的往事太有名了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.35,0:17:44.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為和那種傢伙作戰的報酬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.53,0:17:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,政府又會為我們準備些什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.74,0:17:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概只有IP排名提升以及還算豐厚的成功報酬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.36,0:17:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,該死FUCKIN' 居然讓我們為了那種東西搭上性命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:17:59.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,報酬方面我還可以繼續協商…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.88,0:18:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你根本不明白 BOY
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:02.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是錢的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.52,0:18:07.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那 為我一戰如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.68,0:18:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變態…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.19,0:18:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了你？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.47,0:18:16.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變態說為了他…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.22,0:18:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟然對哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.83,0:18:17.77,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,那也太奇怪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.60,0:18:29.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才多久沒見 你就改頭換面了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事情忘記告訴你了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.92,0:18:35.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可不聽比我弱的傢伙的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.06,0:18:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.06,0:18:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,排名1850位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.15,0:18:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜘蛛型 片桐弓月
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:48.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同為排名1850位
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.27,0:18:50.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,片桐玉樹
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 蒂娜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.43,0:18:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把你也牽扯進來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:56.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 既然要打的話就打贏他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.60,0:18:59.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,陣型DELTA
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.97,0:19:01.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:04.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些在YOU的周圍旋轉的怪東西
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.35,0:19:08.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是貓頭鷹型的蒂娜·斯普朗特
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.80,0:19:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,排名已遭除名 所以沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.47,0:19:14.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,排名300位 里見蓮太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼300位啊 明明是個變態
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.58,0:19:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來吧 一起跳舞吧 BOY！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「焰火扇」！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,錵製的鏈鋸？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.60,0:19:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(349,437)\fs21}Varanium
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.02,0:19:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你發現得太遲了 BOY！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:53.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蜘蛛絲？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.81,0:19:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來如此 那傢伙的墨鏡是為了看這個的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.31,0:19:58.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你已經無法逃脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.78,0:20:01.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去死吧 你這個混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.47,0:20:11.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「隱禪·上下花迷子」！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.60,0:20:18.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.01,0:20:21.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果不是我 早就已經死了 可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.23,0:20:22.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你還活著啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:22.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:28.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妹妹她們的戰鬥差不多也該分出勝負了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.67,0:20:31.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勝負已分了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:33.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看這個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.66,0:20:41.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投降吧 你已經沒有勝算了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.60,0:20:45.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你受傷我也管不著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:01.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:03.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,分出勝負了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.37,0:21:06.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請站起來 弓月小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.73,0:21:11.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.14,0:21:15.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的我 即使參加輔助部隊也只會添麻煩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:17.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有那種事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠將前排名98位的我逼迫到如此地步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.07,0:21:23.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你可以為此感到自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.54,0:21:25.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,9 98位？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.61,0:21:26.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:34.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,片桐弓月小姐 請務必加入哥哥的輔助部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:36.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蒂娜我好喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.63,0:21:38.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超級強大 超級帥氣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.80,0:21:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請嫁給我！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.56,0:21:43.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,合格了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.80,0:21:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這還用問嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.53,0:23:49.52,Comment,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fsp4\be4\bord2}#09  結界的守護者
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.33,0:23:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用害怕原腸動物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.33,0:23:41.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(480,437)\fs21}Gastrea
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.00,0:23:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想給她自由 讓她看看更廣闊的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.95,0:23:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始了 里見！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.23,0:23:47.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是一場沒有光榮也沒有矜持的戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.18,0:23:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不論輸贏都很無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,OP
Comment: 0,0:01:16.50,0:01:19.11,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}ひび割れ　壊れゆく
Comment: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:22.23,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}世界は果てしなく
Comment: 0,0:01:22.52,0:01:25.29,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}未知なる創造が
Comment: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:28.32,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}今秩序をなくしてる
Comment: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:31.69,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}重ね合う痛みが
Comment: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:34.79,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}繰り返す現実
Comment: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:37.72,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}君との毎日が
Comment: 0,0:01:37.81,0:01:41.01,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}その闇に身を投げた
Comment: 0,0:01:41.14,0:01:44.00,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}指し示した道を
Comment: 0,0:01:44.26,0:01:47.21,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}輝かせたいから
Comment: 0,0:01:47.32,0:01:53.08,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}黒いこの銃弾が今すべてを撃ちぬく
Comment: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:56.28,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}赤く燃える　その眼差しに
Comment: 0,0:01:56.37,0:01:59.34,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}熱く響く　命の鼓動を
Comment: 0,0:01:59.42,0:02:04.01,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}強く深く　貫いてゆく　真実を
Comment: 0,0:02:05.53,0:02:08.64,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}傷だらけの心を抱いて
Comment: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:11.67,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}ずっと明日を引き寄せるから
Comment: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:16.50,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}この体にすべてを込めて戦うよ
Comment: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:21.71,ED-J,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}希望を信じて
Comment: 0,0:01:16.50,0:01:19.11,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}世界无休止地
Comment: 0,0:01:19.43,0:01:22.23,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}变得粉碎
Comment: 0,0:01:22.52,0:01:25.29,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}未知的创造
Comment: 0,0:01:25.50,0:01:28.32,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}正在破坏着秩序
Comment: 0,0:01:28.90,0:01:31.69,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}累积的痛苦
Comment: 0,0:01:31.93,0:01:34.79,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}就是重复的现实
Comment: 0,0:01:35.01,0:01:37.72,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}和你度过的每一天
Comment: 0,0:01:37.81,0:01:41.01,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}都投身于这黑暗之中
Comment: 0,0:01:41.14,0:01:44.00,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}因为想要照亮
Comment: 0,0:01:44.26,0:01:47.21,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}指引的路途
Comment: 0,0:01:47.32,0:01:53.08,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}现在我将用这枚黑色的子弹 击穿一切
Comment: 0,0:01:53.18,0:01:56.28,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}火红燃烧　为你的眼神
Comment: 0,0:01:56.37,0:01:59.34,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}热烈奏响  生命的心跳
Comment: 0,0:01:59.42,0:02:04.01,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}强烈深邃地贯穿真实
Comment: 0,0:02:05.53,0:02:08.64,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}怀抱布满伤痕的心
Comment: 0,0:02:08.77,0:02:11.67,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}因为想要永远拥抱明天
Comment: 0,0:02:11.77,0:02:16.50,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}我将身负一切 战斗下去
Comment: 0,0:02:18.12,0:02:21.71,ED-C,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be4}相信着希望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,ED
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.07,0:22:42.55,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}初めはいつだって
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.83,0:22:45.52,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}期待を止められない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:51.00,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}けれどやがて諦めを覚える
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.42,0:22:53.90,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}今を守る盾を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.22,0:22:56.89,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}薬莢に詰め込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.06,0:23:00.38,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}円く壁を切り取った
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:04.57,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}のぞけば
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.00,0:23:12.47,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}終わりが見返してた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.68,0:23:18.47,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}激しい黒に包まれた君の
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.95,0:23:21.72,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}哀情でも心傷でも
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.79,0:23:24.49,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}全部取り込んで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.68,0:23:27.38,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}それすら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.56,0:23:29.96,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}僕の糧にしてみせるさ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.05,0:23:32.74,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}like a lotus
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.21,0:23:34.51,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}だからずっと
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:37.22,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}傍にいて
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.07,0:22:42.55,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}最初無論何時
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.83,0:22:45.52,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}都無法停止期待
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:51.00,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}但我最終學會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.42,0:22:53.90,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}將守護現在的盾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.22,0:22:56.89,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}滿滿地裝入彈殼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.06,0:23:00.38,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}擊穿高牆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.59,0:23:04.57,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}向外窺探
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.00,0:23:12.47,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}才發現終點正向我回望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.68,0:23:18.47,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}連那包裹在濃烈黑色中的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.95,0:23:21.72,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}你的悲哀與心傷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.79,0:23:24.49,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}我都悉數納入懷中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.68,0:23:27.38,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}即使這些
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.56,0:23:29.96,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}我也要將它們變成我的食糧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.05,0:23:32.74,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}like a lotus
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.21,0:23:34.51,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}所以請你一直
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.60,0:23:37.22,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be7}陪伴在我身邊
